RelatedSentence: ( Sequim ) -- Firefighters are battling a blaze at the Baja Cantina restaurant building in the 800 block of West Washington in Sequim .

District 3 Public Information Officer Patrick Young told Newsradio KONP at the scene that a medic crew responding to a medical call drove past the building shortly after 1 p.m. and discovered the fire , calling in additional crews .
Young believes there is significant damage to the building that housed a restaurant and a consignment shop .
Traffic has been diverted from the area by Police and sheriff 's deputies at 9th and Washington on the west side of the fire scene and 7th and Washington on the east side .
